Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是士郎的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有比把圣杯拿到手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.23,0:00:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来实现自己的愿望更好的办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.31,0:00:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想消除这肉眼所看不见的灼伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.76,0:00:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只需接受那圣痕便行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.80,0:00:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫宫士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你作为被选中的Master
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.14,0:00:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有无为此圣杯战争而战斗的觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.13,0:00:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.26,0:01:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样见面已经是第二次了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 这家伙和我们不是一个层次的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.60,0:01:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是伊利雅 伊利雅斯菲尔.冯.阿因兹贝伦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.77,0:01:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样说该明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.03,0:01:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿因兹贝伦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打招呼就到此为止了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你们都会死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.16,0:01:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 杀了你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.96,0:01:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉他们 Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.96,0:01:26.51,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Berserker:狂战士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:41.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢に見ていた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:41.72,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦里再次遇见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:44.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あの日の影に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:44.57,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那日的残影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.61,0:01:50.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屆かない叫び
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.61,0:01:50.38,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法传达到的呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:53.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日の自分は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:53.12,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.64,0:01:56.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なんて描いても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.64,0:01:56.49,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎样描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:02:02.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消えない願いに濡れる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:02:02.59,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会被那永不消逝的祈愿所淋湿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:11.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零れ落ちる欠片を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:11.00,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洒落的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:16.24,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,つかむその手で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:16.24,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用双手紧握
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:22.44,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揺れる心を抱えて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:22.44,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱持着不安的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:30.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳び込んでけ夜へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:30.86,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跃入那无尽的黑夜之中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:36.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かのために生きて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:36.74,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了谁而生存着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.95,0:02:41.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この時が全てで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.95,0:02:41.41,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是将其当成我的全部生命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:42.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いいでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:42.45,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也无怨无悔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:48.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見せかけの自分捨てて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:48.04,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将虚伪的自己就此舍弃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:55.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯ありのままで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:55.12,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只留下仅存的那一份真实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:03:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最强的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎 退后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.61,0:03:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的巨剑在他手中就如同玩具一般
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉他们 干掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.12,0:03:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Berserker 就在那里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一口气干掉她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远阪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.93,0:04:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vier Stil
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ErschieBung
